# Intent
  pa.computeDesired: pure bindings -> per-track trackSpecs. Pins the
  pooled-duplicate collapse, the same-track no-send rule, and the sorted
  slot order the mirror diff depends on for a stable REAPER image.

# Helpers
  @fn binding(over)  @ 10-16

# Cases
  @case 'same-track binding: filter + listen on one spec, no send'  [pure]  @ 21-30
  @case 'cross-track binding fans out by send; pooled duplicates collapse'  [pure]  @ 34-43
  @case 'slots sort by src code / bus code for a stable image'  [pure]  @ 47-56

